race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: TIGER TAILS (1) was well off top last time, finishing 5th (22.75) in a Grade 5 at Gosford. Has a strong winning record here at this journey including three wins. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Can make amends. KENZIES COMET (2) missed the frame last time out when sixth at Gosford from Box four (22.36) but draws same box here as latest win. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Can do much better this time. BIGBAD FRANKY (8) missed the frame latest when seventh at Gosford (22.75) but scored four back at Gosford (22.36). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to feature in the finish. JACK JACK BINKS (7) hit the frame here last start so don't underestimate.
